{"tid":697400,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[G] 黃心美自爆只識C朗","createTime":"2018-06-11T02:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T03:03:03.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"85961c993086dc878384f2e48bec4b2766605bc5","tid":697400,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T02:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180611/large/11ec2p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180611%2Flarge%2F11ec2p11.jpg&h=8bdda42a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n心美昨出席活動時透露將忙於跟球迷睇波。<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤、黃心美與陳俞希（Hailey）等昨日於屯門為全新一輯《Good Night Show全民星戰》宣傳。世界盃即將開鑼，心美將忙於跟球迷睇波，她笑說：「我唔識睇波，我只係識C朗，我都好擔心陪唔到男朋友，世界盃後要分手。」旁邊Hailey指不用擔心，原來她們前日看鐵板神算，師傅指心美感情穩定，而Hailey明年會遇到真愛。<br />\n<br />\n活動尾聲，Hailey捧出蛋糕為阿澤補祝生日。阿澤笑指節目錄影時照爆粗：「我以前喺電台做咗八年節目都冇試過出事，做Live就唔會爆。」"},{"pid":"09539fbf135cb389195e5cebaaafeaf5bd59c39c","tid":697400,"uid":136430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T03:03:03.000Z","msg":"反喇反喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}